WEBVTT

00:18.670 --> 00:19.730
What's wrong, Chu?

00:20.160 --> 00:21.190
Past this forest

00:21.600 --> 00:22.960
is Great Yong's territory.

00:22.960 --> 00:23.600
Yan Xun,

00:24.640 --> 00:25.510
I can't leave.

00:26.960 --> 00:28.070
Ximeng needs me.

00:28.550 --> 00:29.320
Chu,

00:29.960 --> 00:31.690
you've finally figured it out.

00:32.150 --> 00:33.350
I think you're right.

00:34.320 --> 00:36.280
No matter why Zhuge Yue left,

00:36.790 --> 00:38.990
he must have his own things to deal with.

00:39.560 --> 00:41.110
And I have mine.

00:41.520 --> 00:42.850
I need to protect Ximeng

00:43.470 --> 00:45.280
and the people on this land.

00:46.000 --> 00:46.600
Okay.

00:47.150 --> 00:48.030
Come with me.

01:01.200 --> 01:01.920
Chu,

01:02.110 --> 01:04.069
ahead is Xincheng of Great Yong.

01:04.680 --> 01:06.710
It is the border
between Ximeng and Great Yong.

01:06.710 --> 01:08.390
It's Great Yong's northwesternmost city.

01:08.390 --> 01:09.450
Further to the west

01:09.920 --> 01:11.320
are Ximeng and Great Yan.

01:11.480 --> 01:13.430
If we plant kindling
in Ximeng and Great Yan

01:13.430 --> 01:14.400
and use the wind

01:14.970 --> 01:16.970
to launch a fire attack on Xincheng—

01:17.160 --> 01:18.560
the nearest force

01:18.590 --> 01:20.280
is the 20,000 elite troops of Great Yong
stationed

01:20.280 --> 01:21.310
outside Ximeng Pass.

01:21.310 --> 01:22.039
By then,

01:22.310 --> 01:24.110
they will definitely withdraw their army

01:24.110 --> 01:25.190
to save Xincheng.

01:25.760 --> 01:26.430
In this way,

01:27.150 --> 01:28.920
the crisis in Ximeng will be solved auto—

01:28.920 --> 01:29.510
No.

01:29.789 --> 01:30.480
Chu!

01:31.000 --> 01:34.039
This is the best way to make Great Yong
withdraw its troops.

01:34.039 --> 01:36.070
The people of Great Yong
are also human lives.

01:36.070 --> 01:37.229
I can't hurt them.

01:38.840 --> 01:39.479
Yan Xun,

01:40.200 --> 01:40.950
from the very beginning,

01:40.950 --> 01:43.280
you didn't come with me
to chase Zhuge Yue.

01:43.680 --> 01:45.120
You brought me here

01:45.430 --> 01:47.090
to make me listen to your plan.

01:48.400 --> 01:50.229
Chu, have you ever thought about it?

01:50.229 --> 01:52.430
The reason you can maintain this stalemate

01:52.430 --> 01:54.479
is that Great Yong
has not launched an attack.

01:54.479 --> 01:56.070
If they find a new excuse

01:56.200 --> 01:57.660
to occupy Ximeng by force,

01:57.870 --> 01:58.800
the Ximeng Army,

01:59.520 --> 02:01.120
even with the Great Yan Army,

02:01.510 --> 02:03.350
will be no match for Great Yong.

02:13.150 --> 02:13.950
Your Majesty.

02:18.910 --> 02:21.370
The Lanchuan Tribe
actually dared to rebel?

02:21.750 --> 02:24.150
You originally came to Ximeng
to obtain the black gold mine.

02:24.150 --> 02:25.840
But under Helian Ling's name,

02:25.840 --> 02:27.170
you borrowed a large number of troops
from the Hongchuan

02:27.170 --> 02:29.150
and Lanchuan Tribes to support Ximeng.

02:29.150 --> 02:30.520
You went back on your word.

02:30.520 --> 02:32.150
Even if the Lanchuan Tribe
hadn't rebelled,

02:32.150 --> 02:35.410
I'm afraid you wouldn't have a good ending
when you return.

02:39.180 --> 02:40.440
Wait here for a moment.

02:40.630 --> 02:44.490
Our general needs to say a few words
to His Majesty before coming over.

02:51.800 --> 02:54.000
I have already taken away their troops.

02:54.720 --> 02:56.280
Why did they still have
such military strength?

02:56.280 --> 02:58.840
Elder Lanchuan
traded their Yunxian and Jixian

02:58.840 --> 03:00.770
for 10,000 people from Great Yong.

03:00.800 --> 03:03.290
In less than half a month,
they took the west of Lexian.

03:03.290 --> 03:05.420
He dared to collude with the Yong army?

03:05.960 --> 03:08.290
I will go back now,
reclaim these 2 cities,

03:08.840 --> 03:10.750
and then kill that old man
as a sacrifice to our flag!

03:10.750 --> 03:11.470
You think,

03:11.960 --> 03:13.680
after everything that has happened,
Great Yan

03:13.680 --> 03:15.410
can take back these two cities?

03:25.470 --> 03:26.800
General Huan has ordered

03:26.800 --> 03:27.910
that you may only rest here

03:27.910 --> 03:28.910
and are not allowed to go over there.

03:28.910 --> 03:31.540
Your General Huan's orders
don't work on me.

03:44.240 --> 03:44.960
Chu!

03:48.960 --> 03:49.560
Chu!

03:49.800 --> 03:50.430
Chu,

03:51.310 --> 03:52.120
are you alright?

03:52.120 --> 03:52.710
Chu!

03:55.470 --> 03:56.120
Huan Huan,

03:56.590 --> 03:57.710
what are you going to do?

03:57.710 --> 03:58.910
I'm going to trade her

03:58.960 --> 04:00.520
for Yunxian and Jixian.

04:00.680 --> 04:01.560
Not only that.

04:01.630 --> 04:03.630
Right now, the Emperor,
the Thirteenth Prince,

04:03.630 --> 04:05.380
and Princess Protector of the State
of Great Yong all want her.

04:05.380 --> 04:06.570
As long as we hand her over,

04:06.570 --> 04:08.280
we can get Yunxian and Jixian back,

04:08.280 --> 04:10.120
take back half of the black gold mines
in Ximeng,

04:10.120 --> 04:11.150
and bring the war to an end.

04:11.150 --> 04:13.150
Buying time for Great Yan to recover

04:13.310 --> 04:14.970
is what we need most right now.

04:24.480 --> 04:26.480
What makes you think I will agree to this?

04:26.480 --> 04:28.540
Because it's not just about 2 cities.

04:29.240 --> 04:30.840
It's also about your throne.

04:31.920 --> 04:33.000
What did you say?

04:33.750 --> 04:35.060
Over the past two years,

04:35.060 --> 04:36.210
the 13 tribes of Great Yan

04:36.210 --> 04:37.830
have been rebelling one after another.

04:37.830 --> 04:40.159
Are you going to kill
all the tribe elders?

04:40.430 --> 04:41.560
Yunxian and Jixian

04:41.560 --> 04:43.310
are the military fortresses
on the border of Great Yan.

04:43.310 --> 04:44.720
If you don't take back these 2 cities,

04:44.720 --> 04:47.000
with the tribe elders of Great Yan
not submitting to you

04:47.000 --> 04:49.120
and Biantang and Great Yong
eyeing us hungrily,

04:49.120 --> 04:50.310
do you really think this throne

04:50.310 --> 04:51.440
will still be yours?

04:53.159 --> 04:54.800
What if I don't agree?

04:56.070 --> 04:57.270
What will you do?

05:00.480 --> 05:01.430
Kill me

05:02.070 --> 05:03.730
and take the throne yourself?

05:06.680 --> 05:08.430
You've already killed me once.

05:09.510 --> 05:10.480
For Great Yan

05:11.480 --> 05:12.560
and the old King,

05:12.950 --> 05:15.480
what makes you think
I wouldn't dare kill you?

06:38.480 --> 06:43.600
[REBIRTH]

06:44.250 --> 06:46.690
[Episode 34]

06:46.750 --> 06:47.780
[Lingfeng Hall]

06:58.230 --> 07:02.140
[In Memory of My Grandfather,
Zhuge Muqing]

07:07.680 --> 07:08.480
Young Master.

07:08.560 --> 07:10.600
The convoy
for the Master's ancestral rites is ready.

07:10.600 --> 07:15.530
The mourning robes have also been distributed
to each branch according to regulations.

07:22.360 --> 07:24.750
Is Grandfather's study still in use?

07:24.870 --> 07:25.600
No.

07:26.160 --> 07:27.310
Now that the Master is gone,

07:27.310 --> 07:28.530
it has long been locked.

07:28.530 --> 07:29.990
No one goes there anymore.

09:19.910 --> 09:23.080
As expected of the grandson
I personally trained—

09:24.720 --> 09:27.240
you figured it out so quickly.

09:51.320 --> 09:52.200
So...

09:54.600 --> 09:57.000
this was all your plan?

09:59.510 --> 10:00.360
Why?

10:01.270 --> 10:02.730
If I hadn't faked my death,

10:03.440 --> 10:06.240
would you have come back
to Qingshan Manor with me?

10:06.480 --> 10:07.910
Since you are fine,

10:09.030 --> 10:10.390
I don't need to stay.

10:13.270 --> 10:15.360
Do you think you can walk out of here?

10:19.550 --> 10:21.790
Yue Shiyi just died,

10:22.240 --> 10:23.570
and you have forgotten?

10:23.790 --> 10:25.080
Not just Yue Shiyi.

10:25.720 --> 10:28.650
There were also the 3 Moon Guards
killed by Zhao Yang.

10:29.750 --> 10:31.480
You should know better than I do

10:31.840 --> 10:33.480
why they died.

10:34.510 --> 10:35.360
Today,

10:36.320 --> 10:38.650
if you take one step
out of Qingshan Manor,

10:39.390 --> 10:41.440
His Majesty, Zhao Yang,

10:41.790 --> 10:42.960
and Muhe Lie—

10:43.750 --> 10:45.480
which of them would let you go?

10:46.550 --> 10:49.150
And which of them
would let the Zhuge family go?

10:49.440 --> 10:51.000
So this was your plan.

10:52.200 --> 10:53.330
You faked your death

10:54.510 --> 10:57.080
to make me
take over Qingshan Manor from you.

10:58.720 --> 11:01.320
From the moment I stepped into
Jinsheng Palace

11:01.440 --> 11:02.570
and saw His Majesty,

11:03.870 --> 11:05.600
even if I discover the truth,

11:07.150 --> 11:08.390
I can't change the fact

11:08.390 --> 11:10.670
that I've already taken over
Qingshan Manor

11:10.670 --> 11:12.750
and can never escape Great Yong.

11:13.480 --> 11:14.790
Muhe Lie has reported

11:15.600 --> 11:17.480
your betrayal of Great Yong

11:17.960 --> 11:20.560
and the things you did in Ximeng
to His Majesty.

11:21.120 --> 11:22.580
If I hadn't faked my death,

11:22.600 --> 11:25.200
would His Majesty
have spared your life so easily?

11:25.200 --> 11:27.030
Why did I go to Ximeng Pass?

11:28.270 --> 11:30.000
It was to trade Chu Qiao's life

11:30.670 --> 11:32.470
for His Majesty sparing you.

11:32.820 --> 11:34.900
But you refused to take that path.

11:35.270 --> 11:36.030
Yue,

11:37.150 --> 11:39.240
you forced me to do this.

12:05.670 --> 12:06.470
Didn't you...

12:08.510 --> 12:10.240
lose your martial arts ability

12:11.390 --> 12:12.750
and become crippled?

12:12.750 --> 12:16.550
Qingshan Manor has studied
the world's strangest poisons for years.

12:16.550 --> 12:18.600
There is no poison we cannot cure.

12:19.390 --> 12:20.200
I know

12:20.510 --> 12:22.910
you always wanted
to abolish Qingshan Manor.

12:22.910 --> 12:23.790
But...

12:24.750 --> 12:27.670
you couldn't even handle
this little trick of mine.

14:17.870 --> 14:18.600
Yue!

14:18.970 --> 14:20.780
I trained you myself.

14:27.720 --> 14:29.240
You will never defeat me,

14:29.750 --> 14:31.320
nor Qingshan Manor.

15:15.120 --> 15:16.000
Yue,

15:16.630 --> 15:17.960
with such little skill,

15:18.670 --> 15:21.000
you think you can abolish Qingshan Manor?

15:21.270 --> 15:23.730
You can't even protect
your own Moon Guards.

16:09.000 --> 16:09.870
Why?

16:21.390 --> 16:23.980
Once you are a member of Qingshan Manor,

16:25.240 --> 16:28.360
you can never leave Qingshan Manor.

16:29.200 --> 16:33.480
Qingshan Manor is my tomb,

16:35.120 --> 16:36.750
and yours too.

16:37.840 --> 16:39.630
This is destiny.

16:50.870 --> 16:52.080
Thank you...

16:54.120 --> 16:55.240
Yue.

16:58.100 --> 17:00.390
Thank you for personally

17:02.870 --> 17:04.310
killing me here.

17:05.240 --> 17:06.880
I want your heart...

17:07.790 --> 17:08.750
to stay...

17:10.720 --> 17:12.380
in Qingshan Manor forever...

17:15.720 --> 17:17.720
as atonement.

21:26.510 --> 21:27.440
Zhuge Yue?

21:27.640 --> 21:28.570
Why are you here?

21:28.880 --> 21:29.740
What about you?

21:30.790 --> 21:33.030
Aren't you supposed
to be stationed at the border?

21:33.030 --> 21:34.360
Why did you bring troops

21:35.160 --> 21:36.960
and sneak into Zhenhuangcheng?

21:38.400 --> 21:39.270
You don't know

21:40.480 --> 21:42.200
what I've been through.

21:43.510 --> 21:44.770
That's what happened.

21:45.350 --> 21:46.830
All my trusted subordinates—

21:46.830 --> 21:49.440
1 lieutenant, 3 guards,

21:50.440 --> 21:52.510
and the officers including commandants,
captains, and generals—

21:52.510 --> 21:53.720
25 people in total—

21:54.270 --> 21:55.880
were executed on the spot.

21:56.310 --> 21:57.590
And I could only hide in the dark,

21:57.590 --> 21:58.790
watching helplessly

21:59.400 --> 22:00.860
and unable to do anything.

22:03.550 --> 22:05.710
Zhao Yang framed you
for such a serious crime

22:05.710 --> 22:07.240
as colluding with Great Yan.

22:07.240 --> 22:09.700
Does the Emperor of Great Yong
know about it?

22:11.240 --> 22:12.440
So what if he does?

22:14.270 --> 22:16.200
My father is cold and ruthless,

22:16.880 --> 22:18.260
stubborn and suspicious.

22:18.260 --> 22:21.190
Over the years,
he has been extremely wary of me

22:21.210 --> 22:22.350
and tested me in every possible way.

22:22.350 --> 22:24.720
Compared to Zhao Yang, what he has done

22:25.310 --> 22:27.030
is even worse.

22:27.440 --> 22:30.170
He let Zhao Yang turn against me,
his own brother,

22:30.720 --> 22:33.440
just as he is using the Muhe family

22:33.440 --> 22:35.040
to suppress Qingshan Manor.

22:35.640 --> 22:39.040
Over the years, the 4 major noble families
in Zhenhuangcheng

22:39.270 --> 22:41.470
have never stopped fighting, locked in

22:41.550 --> 22:45.810
a life-and-death struggle, each rising
and falling at the other's expense.

22:45.830 --> 22:47.960
It's all part of his schemes for power.

22:48.070 --> 22:51.070
I originally just wanted to serve him
wholeheartedly,

22:51.070 --> 22:53.870
even if it meant assisting Zhao Yang
in the future.

22:54.310 --> 22:56.200
But he wouldn't even give me

22:56.200 --> 22:57.270
a way out.

22:57.920 --> 22:58.590
But,

22:59.510 --> 23:01.640
the imperial guard of Zhenhuangcheng

23:02.350 --> 23:04.010
is 10 times larger than yours.

23:04.070 --> 23:05.270
Have you ever thought

23:05.960 --> 23:07.560
that once you take this path,

23:08.400 --> 23:09.800
there's no turning back?

23:15.920 --> 23:17.550
That's why I need your help.

23:19.070 --> 23:20.530
I can't turn back anymore.

23:27.160 --> 23:27.920
You want me

23:29.160 --> 23:30.490
to join forces with you?

23:30.750 --> 23:31.550
Zhuge Yue,

23:33.400 --> 23:34.920
I have no way back.

23:35.550 --> 23:36.480
Neither do you,

23:37.400 --> 23:38.070
do you?

23:51.070 --> 23:51.870
Your Majesty,

23:52.310 --> 23:54.840
further ahead
is the territory of Great Yong.

23:55.590 --> 23:56.850
I have selected a troop

23:56.880 --> 23:59.140
to escort you back to Great Yan from here.

24:04.480 --> 24:06.210
I am still the King of Great Yan.

24:06.440 --> 24:08.700
Since we will negotiate with Great Yong,

24:08.880 --> 24:12.550
you can't represent me, can you?

24:14.440 --> 24:17.350
You've already fed Chu
the muscle-softening powder

24:17.350 --> 24:19.410
and sent so many people to escort her.

24:19.830 --> 24:21.430
What are you worrying about?

24:22.510 --> 24:23.070
Alright.

24:23.640 --> 24:24.790
You can go with us,

24:25.350 --> 24:28.270
but please do not carry any weapons.

24:46.310 --> 24:47.170
General Cheng.

24:47.400 --> 24:48.270
My Lady,

24:48.680 --> 24:49.680
why are you here?

24:58.110 --> 25:00.370
I want to choose a suitable horse to ride.

25:00.440 --> 25:01.920
Could you help me?

25:22.480 --> 25:24.440
This is a pony from Great Yan.

25:24.750 --> 25:27.550
Although it is not as tall
as the Huolei horses,

25:28.240 --> 25:29.830
it rides smoothly,

25:30.350 --> 25:31.810
with a gentle temperament

25:32.070 --> 25:33.590
and great endurance,

25:34.200 --> 25:36.800
capable of traveling 100 li a day
without rest.

25:37.110 --> 25:38.910
Would you like to try it, My Lady?

25:53.790 --> 25:54.400
Helian!

25:59.030 --> 26:00.960
Take me to the place you mentioned.

26:39.400 --> 26:39.960
Come.

26:58.480 --> 27:00.000
Yesterday, General Huan recalled
the 5,000 elite cavalry

27:00.000 --> 27:03.200
bestowed on her by His Majesty
from the Snowy Region Tribe

27:03.350 --> 27:05.790
and stationed them
north of the Capital and Lexian,

27:05.790 --> 27:08.390
together with
the Capital's Black Eagle Army.

27:08.880 --> 27:12.080
The rebels of the Lanchuan Tribe
have all been taken down.

27:13.440 --> 27:16.040
His Majesty has gone
to reinforce Ximeng Pass.

27:16.790 --> 27:18.790
Great Yan can take this opportunity

27:19.310 --> 27:20.510
to unite with Ximeng.

27:21.510 --> 27:23.000
Once Great Yong fears

27:23.270 --> 27:25.070
our combined power with Ximeng,

27:25.110 --> 27:27.960
securing several years
for Great Yan to catch its breath

27:27.960 --> 27:29.160
will not be a problem.

27:35.790 --> 27:38.480
By then, there will be renewal,

27:39.240 --> 27:41.000
and the people will live in peace.

27:41.000 --> 27:42.590
Have you ever thought about

27:43.750 --> 27:45.270
living in a different way?

27:47.000 --> 27:48.270
I was born in Great Yan,

27:49.030 --> 27:50.160
grew up in Great Yan,

27:51.110 --> 27:53.110
and have been fighting for Great Yan

27:53.580 --> 27:55.240
and His Majesty my whole life.

27:55.960 --> 27:58.290
I have never thought about anything else.

28:02.510 --> 28:05.310
I was never valued by the Helian family
since childhood,

28:05.310 --> 28:07.030
and I was often bullied by my clansmen.

28:07.030 --> 28:08.030
My brother

28:08.440 --> 28:10.700
only saw me as a tool
for wealth and power.

28:11.590 --> 28:13.850
I dreamed of making something of myself,

28:14.070 --> 28:17.270
because only then could I earn
the family's recognition.

28:17.830 --> 28:21.290
Now I have become
the Princess Consort of Great Yan as I wished,

28:21.510 --> 28:23.510
bringing glory to the Helian Tribe.

28:24.030 --> 28:25.160
My brother has also obtained

28:25.160 --> 28:26.890
the wealth and power he wanted.

28:28.880 --> 28:31.740
That time, my brother tricked me
into going to Tubu,

28:32.510 --> 28:34.040
and Tubu tried to harass me.

28:36.680 --> 28:39.680
I thought I was going to die
in the Capital of Great Yan,

28:42.000 --> 28:43.590
but you appeared

28:44.070 --> 28:44.920
and saved me.

28:50.000 --> 28:52.060
The day the Lanchuan Tribe rebelled,

28:52.640 --> 28:53.920
you saved me again.

29:04.310 --> 29:07.640
You made me understand
the meaning of living.

29:08.590 --> 29:09.960
Great Yan, Great Yong,

29:10.590 --> 29:12.390
and the rise and fall of my tribe—

29:12.790 --> 29:14.790
none of them has anything to do with me.

29:14.790 --> 29:16.790
I just want to live the rest of my life

29:17.110 --> 29:18.350
the way I choose.

29:24.790 --> 29:27.250
What kind of life do you want to live,
My Lady?

29:36.350 --> 29:37.610
I want to move forward.

29:38.070 --> 29:40.790
I want to live a life
that truly belongs to me,

29:41.350 --> 29:43.350
finding a place where no one knows me

29:43.400 --> 29:45.830
and living peacefully and freely,

29:46.750 --> 29:49.240
without benefits or disputes.

29:54.310 --> 29:55.270
What about you?

29:56.440 --> 29:58.440
What kind of life do you want to live?

30:03.680 --> 30:04.400
Helian.

30:06.070 --> 30:06.790
I...

30:28.510 --> 30:32.130
♪ The dust in the world ♪

30:32.650 --> 30:36.130
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

30:36.830 --> 30:39.630
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

30:40.470 --> 30:41.810
♪ And not be scared? ♪

30:41.000 --> 30:44.000
Your sincerity toward His Majesty
is rare and valuable.

30:41.840 --> 30:43.850
♪ A slight ripple ♪

30:44.040 --> 30:47.630
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

30:45.400 --> 30:46.160
I know

30:47.200 --> 30:48.550
that no matter what,

30:47.910 --> 30:51.280
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

30:49.400 --> 30:51.600
you would never betray him or Great Yan.

30:52.250 --> 30:55.090
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

30:53.110 --> 30:54.070
Your faith

30:54.720 --> 30:55.640
and your life

30:55.750 --> 30:59.130
♪ Let it be ♪

30:56.310 --> 30:57.710
both belong to Great Yan.

31:00.210 --> 31:03.640
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

31:04.110 --> 31:07.130
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

31:07.520 --> 31:09.150
♪ Go weaving ♪

31:09.470 --> 31:14.420
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

31:15.040 --> 31:17.580
♪ We face ♪

31:17.610 --> 31:21.460
♪ The heavy thunderstorm together ♪

31:22.620 --> 31:25.350
♪ Even with extreme pain ♪

31:25.370 --> 31:30.140
♪ We don't even wince ♪

31:30.660 --> 31:33.510
♪ Why in this world ♪

31:33.540 --> 31:38.260
♪ The staunchest heart
and strongest soul ♪

31:37.270 --> 31:38.030
Helian!

31:38.930 --> 31:45.110
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

31:40.440 --> 31:42.640
Thank you for the horse, General Cheng!

31:46.700 --> 31:58.080
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

32:08.000 --> 32:08.800
General Huan,

32:09.070 --> 32:12.030
I have been ordered
to welcome you into the city here.

32:12.880 --> 32:15.240
But it's getting late today.

32:15.590 --> 32:17.400
The Thirteenth Prince has ordered

32:17.400 --> 32:20.130
that you go to the posthouse
to settle down first.

32:20.400 --> 32:21.460
Thank you, My Lord.

32:21.550 --> 32:22.680
Please lead the way.

32:23.480 --> 32:24.830
Sorry, General.

32:25.160 --> 32:26.920
The troop cannot enter the city.

32:26.920 --> 32:28.320
His Highness has ordered

32:28.350 --> 32:30.480
that you are only to take
the guilty slave, Chu Qiao,

32:30.480 --> 32:32.470
and three guards with you.

32:32.610 --> 32:33.610
The rest of the troops

32:33.610 --> 32:36.340
must be stationed
20 li outside Zhenhuangcheng.

32:36.550 --> 32:40.150
Is this how Zhao Yang made arrangements
for the King of Great Yan?

32:40.830 --> 32:42.240
His Highness' intention was to

32:42.240 --> 32:46.240
prevent the people of the city from seeing
the troops of Great Yan again.

32:51.400 --> 32:53.160
You three, come with me.

32:53.400 --> 32:55.110
The rest of you, stay here.

33:18.660 --> 33:22.280
[Taihe Palace]

33:23.110 --> 33:23.970
Your Highness.

33:24.440 --> 33:25.880
Our agreement terms

33:26.200 --> 33:27.400
were sent to Zhenhuangcheng

33:27.400 --> 33:29.000
by a messenger three days ago.

33:29.000 --> 33:30.600
I wonder if you have read them

33:30.920 --> 33:31.510
and

33:32.030 --> 33:33.270
have any opinions.

33:35.240 --> 33:36.100
Your Highness.

33:36.240 --> 33:37.100
Your Highness!

33:41.790 --> 33:42.720
What did you say?

33:43.270 --> 33:44.790
Our agreement document—

33:45.030 --> 33:46.440
have you read it?

33:47.500 --> 33:48.100
I haven't.

33:49.240 --> 33:50.480
Go ahead. I'm listening.

33:50.480 --> 33:52.550
According to our previous discussion,

33:52.550 --> 33:54.240
we will offer Chu Qiao to Great Yong.

33:54.240 --> 33:55.920
Great Yong must keep its promise

33:55.920 --> 33:57.520
to return Yunxian and Jixian

33:57.640 --> 33:59.790
and call a truce with Great Yan
on this basis.

33:59.790 --> 34:00.850
Within five years,

34:00.960 --> 34:02.640
Great Yong shall not interfere
in Great Yan's internal affairs

34:02.640 --> 34:03.830
in any form.

34:04.530 --> 34:05.760
Where is Princess Chun'er?

34:05.760 --> 34:07.270
Where did Princess Chun'er go?

34:07.270 --> 34:08.190
Your Highness.

34:08.360 --> 34:10.190
Princess Chun'er just sent someone to say

34:10.190 --> 34:11.710
she went to the hot spring today

34:11.710 --> 34:12.840
and will come later.

34:13.070 --> 34:13.730
Hot spring?

34:15.630 --> 34:16.760
Hot spring is good.

34:16.800 --> 34:18.280
It nourishes the skin.

34:19.320 --> 34:20.960
A beauty in a hot spring...

34:21.920 --> 34:22.920
Keep going.

34:24.920 --> 34:27.380
In addition,
there is an additional clause.

34:27.670 --> 34:29.670
After Great Yong takes down Ximeng,

34:29.800 --> 34:30.960
half of the black gold mine in Ximeng

34:30.960 --> 34:32.550
will belong to Great Yan.

34:34.630 --> 34:35.489
Anything else?

34:35.800 --> 34:36.320
No.

34:36.510 --> 34:37.670
Then let it be.

34:45.320 --> 34:46.280
Your Highness.

34:59.590 --> 35:00.790
Sister, you're here?

35:09.630 --> 35:11.480
How could you let them go

35:12.000 --> 35:14.000
without even reading the document?

35:14.070 --> 35:15.400
Sister, you can read it.

35:29.280 --> 35:30.670
Everything else can be discussed further,

35:30.670 --> 35:32.930
but we can't give you the black gold mine.

35:33.150 --> 35:34.210
Princess Chun'er.

35:34.840 --> 35:36.320
Every condition on this

35:36.670 --> 35:38.330
has already been agreed upon.

35:42.290 --> 35:43.150
Your Highness.

35:43.710 --> 35:45.960
Great Yong and Great Yan
have been fighting for so many years.

35:45.960 --> 35:47.760
The national treasury is tight.

35:48.000 --> 35:49.920
If you can hand over this black gold mine

35:49.920 --> 35:51.710
intact to His Majesty,

35:52.030 --> 35:55.400
he will definitely reward you again.

35:58.190 --> 36:00.480
Okay, I'll listen to you.

36:03.550 --> 36:05.610
We won't give you the black gold mine.

36:06.510 --> 36:08.550
Since you have gone back on your word,

36:08.550 --> 36:10.810
we don't have to keep our promise either.

36:11.280 --> 36:12.320
We won't

36:13.230 --> 36:14.710
make this deal.

36:15.550 --> 36:16.150
Wait.

36:17.070 --> 36:18.880
Great Yan can give up the black gold mine,

36:18.880 --> 36:20.400
but the five-year truce

36:20.630 --> 36:22.630
must be extended by another 5 years.

36:24.760 --> 36:25.670
General Huan,

36:27.800 --> 36:29.600
are you making a decision for me?

36:30.030 --> 36:30.830
Your Majesty,

36:31.190 --> 36:32.510
I am making a decision
for the elders of Great Yan

36:32.510 --> 36:33.960
and its people.

36:34.230 --> 36:36.150
I hope you can also think for them

36:36.360 --> 36:37.760
and approve my decision.

36:37.800 --> 36:38.360
Alright.

36:38.960 --> 36:40.440
Then it's a deal.

36:41.030 --> 36:43.320
From now on, Great Yong and Great Yan

36:43.710 --> 36:45.570
will not fight again for 10 years.

36:59.670 --> 37:00.440
Chu.

37:08.070 --> 37:09.920
Chu Qiao is not here anymore.

37:17.440 --> 37:18.360
Where is Chu?

37:18.800 --> 37:20.400
After today's negotiation,

37:20.400 --> 37:23.060
I handed her over
to that princess of Great Yong.

37:27.360 --> 37:28.070
Yan Xun!

37:31.000 --> 37:32.530
Don't be stubborn anymore.

37:32.670 --> 37:33.550
It's over.

37:34.760 --> 37:36.160
There is no turning back.

37:37.320 --> 37:38.850
Go back to Great Yan with me.

38:06.800 --> 38:07.550
Princess Chun'er,

38:07.550 --> 38:08.480
Chu Qiao is here.

38:19.760 --> 38:22.360
You were a slave in Zhenhuangcheng
for so long,

38:22.880 --> 38:24.910
but you've never been here, have you?

38:24.910 --> 38:27.070
It's been a long time since we last met

38:27.400 --> 38:28.920
in Biantang.

38:29.510 --> 38:32.150
I thought you had figured it out.

38:34.960 --> 38:36.710
How could you say such things?

38:37.400 --> 38:38.550
Don't you know

38:39.480 --> 38:40.670
why I'm like this?

38:41.510 --> 38:43.640
Everything I had was destroyed by you.

38:45.440 --> 38:46.760
But it's all good now.

38:47.360 --> 38:49.150
You have nothing, just like me.

38:50.630 --> 38:51.400
How is it?

38:51.670 --> 38:54.130
Does it feel good
to be betrayed by everyone?

38:56.910 --> 38:58.620
We both have nothing.

39:00.110 --> 39:01.170
You're not afraid,

39:02.400 --> 39:03.480
so why should I be?

39:05.630 --> 39:07.090
You are just a lowly slave.

39:07.230 --> 39:09.230
What makes you think we are the same?

39:11.960 --> 39:13.880
How is it, General Chu?

39:14.360 --> 39:17.360
The muscle-softening powder works well,
doesn't it?

39:21.190 --> 39:22.320
Lock her up!

39:31.400 --> 39:34.000
Your Highness,
someone requests an audience.

40:02.020 --> 40:02.750
Huan Huan,

40:04.060 --> 40:06.590
I will definitely
become the master of Zhenhuangcheng.

40:06.590 --> 40:08.070
I hope you can help me

40:08.880 --> 40:10.010
take back Great Yan.

40:10.190 --> 40:10.800
Chun'er!

40:12.250 --> 40:14.870
An ominous sign. It's an ominous sign!

40:14.920 --> 40:15.550
Yan Xun,

40:16.230 --> 40:17.550
did I make the wrong choice?

40:17.550 --> 40:19.000
Qingshan Manor, hear my command!

40:19.000 --> 40:21.190
Capture the King of Great Yan
and Chu Qiao at all costs!
